text: Ekaterina Romanenko Raevskaia (born 23 December 1993) is a Russian volleyball player. == Career == She played at the 2015 Summer Universiade, 2015 FIVB World Grand Prix, 2015 Montreux Volley Masters, and 2017 FIVB Volleyball Women's Club World Championship. She played for WVC Dynamo Kazan. == References == == Other websites == * BVB profile Category:1993 births Category:Russian volleyball players Category:Living people
